org.moeaframework.problem.tsplib

Class TSPExample

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.moeaframework.problem.tsplib.TSPExample

  • public class TSPExample
extends java.lang.Object
    Demonstration of optimizing a TSP problem using the MOEA Framework optimization library (http://www.moeaframework.org/). A window will appear showing the progress of the optimization algorithm. The window will contain a visual representation of the TSP problem instance, with a thick red line indicating the best tour found by the optimization algorithm. Light gray lines are the other (sub-optimal) tours in the population.
